data.description: **Seller has had all the main areas freshly painted!** This home is everything you've been waiting for! In the highly sought after North Paulding school district, this home is one of the few in the community that sits on a full unfinished basement! The basement has already been plumbed and a bathroom has been framed! It has the potential to be an in law suite, or separate apartment, the opportunities are endless! The gazebo on the back porch will stay and makes for a perfect place to stay cool on hot summer days! The back yard is spacious and level and the wooden privacy fence is in impeccable condition. There is a covered area that's enclosed to the side of the deck, great for lawn equipment or storage - This is the perfect option for a family with children or pets! The living area has a custom shiplap accent wall that adds beautiful character to the home! The kitchen features granite countertops, an island/bar, and stainless steel appliances. Upstairs you will find 4 bedrooms and a bonus room that would be perfect for an office or playroom! The master bedroom is oversized and has a sitting room as well as a huge walk-in closet. The master bathroom has double vanities, and a separate shower and garden tub. Aside from this awesome home, the community has so much to offer: sidewalks, swim/tennis, a clubhouse, and more! Situated near restaurants, shopping, hiking, entertainment, major roadways, and world-class medical centers, Cedar Mill Subdivision is practically perfect in every way. Come see for yourself and live the North Paulding Lifestyle!
